            "author_color": "#000000",
            "testimonial_1": "This company saved my life.They are the best. The hormone creams are so easy to use. Everyone is great and willing to help you. Definitely recommend 🙂",
            "author_1": "Naynaz O.",
            "testimonial_2": "I was a broken woman when I stepped into Dr. Tammy’s office. After a very in depth conversation I felt the hope that I had been looking for. After a lot of testing she sat me down and explained what the problem areas were and what I needed. Bio-identical hormones changed my life!She is called the hormone queen for a reason!If you’re on the fence about what to do, just go see he and hear what she has to say. You won’t regret it! We love her!",
            "author_2": "Sheila p.",
            "testimonial_3": "Life is sooooo much better when the hormones are good!!! Not to mention that everyone around you is better when your hormones are good! 🤗 This book puts it in plain English and Dr. Tammy is an amazing advocate for your health- mind, body, and soul!",
            "author_3": "Dayna C.",
            "testimonial_4": "I have been on hormone therapy for about 6 months and I could do life without it …. Not nice anyway…I have energy life I did years ago…my hair is as thick as when I was in my. 20’s and all around feel better.. I definitely recommend",
            "author_4": "Paula S.",
            "testimonial_5": "I was introduced to Hormone Bliss at the end of 2024 and started the bio-identical hormones in January of 2025. I do notice the effects! I am sleeping better and have learned so much about hormones in general. I have one of Dr. Tammy’s books that explains so much about hormones and have found it very helpful. Also, one of the supplements offered through the Hormone Bliss website has helped my fibromyalgia symptoms immensely. Dr. Tammy and Hormone Bliss has been a definite plus in my life. Thank you, Dr. Tammy!",
            "author_5": "Heidi S.",
            "testimonial_6": "The creams are great. Owner is very knowledgeable and answers questions thoroughly.The once a month zoom calls are a bonus! Highly recommend.",
            "author_6": "Michele H."
